        public static TypeDefinitionContainer cloneTypeList(int depth,
                                    boolean includePropertyDefinitions,
                                    TypeDefinitionContainer tdc,
                                    TypeDefinitionContainer parent,
                                    boolean cmis11)
        traverse tree and replace each need node with a clone. remove properties on clone if requested, cut children of clone if depth is exceeded.
        Parameters:
        depth - levels of children to copy
        includePropertyDefinitions - indicates with or without property definitions
        tdc - type definition to clone
        parent - parent container where to add clone as child
        Returns:
        cloned type definition
